<h2 class="bold font-l">"Sinking Peril"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
&quot;Sinking Peril&quot; has Sly scaling Clockwerk's tower as it sinks into the lava, the magnatronic support field keeping it up having been destroyed in the previous mission. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="9oyz8b" data-video-descrip="In &amp;quot;Copy Cats&amp;quot;, Sly has to use his thief costume to scale a wrecked ship on the verge of sinking into The Tiger's cell." data-video-title="&quot;Copy Cats&quot;" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/9oyz8b_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/9oyz8b.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/SinkingShipScenario" data-video-tropename="Sinking Ship Scenario" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/SlyCooperThievesInTime,Recap/SlyCooperThievesInTimeMission05FortyThieves" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/9oyz8b.jpg">
